data.description: USDA, VA, FHA eligible! No HOA fees here! A newer metal roof, vinyl siding and fresh paint throughout this beautiful 4bd, 3 bathroom home with almost 2,000 sq ft of living space sets you on the path to get excited for a home that's completely move-in ready! All appliances, leased water softener, and washer/dryer are negotiable! Park in the back yard that leads straight into the kitchen on grocery day or park in the front that takes you straight into the sitting room. Wait until you see the size of the living room! The kitchen offers eat in options or separate dining, room for an island and a pantry if you need additional storage and stainless steel appliances! You have lots of options here! Main floor: 3 bedrooms, 1 full and 1 half bathroom, laundry, sitting and living room, coat closet, kitchen and dining room. Upstairs: master suite with a full bathroom and a walk-in closet! Outside: 2 sheds covered, front and back porch, 6ft tall private, vinyl fencing all on a beautiful corner lot!
